---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with DSA Vault — report issues, suggest improvements, or say hello.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-vault-text mb-6">Contact</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:text-vault-text prose-p:text-vault-muted prose-a:text-vault-primary prose-strong:text-vault-text prose-li:text-vault-muted">
      <p>
        Have a question, found an error in a solution, or want to suggest a problem to cover? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@dsavault.in">contact@dsavault.in</a></li>
        <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> DSA Vault (comment on any video)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Report an Issue</h2>
      <p>
        Found a bug in a solution or an error in an explanation? Please include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The problem number and name</li>
        <li>Which section has the issue (brute force, optimal, etc.)</li>
        <li>A brief description of the error</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Suggest a Problem</h2>
      <p>
        Want us to cover a specific LeetCode problem? Send us the problem number and we'll prioritize it in our content roadmap.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
